+ yaml-cpp
- Download
yaml-cpp is obtained from:
  https://code.google.com/p/yaml-cpp/
via hg:
  $ hg clone https://code.google.com/p/yaml-cpp/

- Install
  $ cd yaml-cpp
  $ mkdir build
  $ cd build
  $ ccmake ..
    BUILD_SHARED_LIBS = ON or OFF
  $ make

- Usage
See the tutorial:
  https://code.google.com/p/yaml-cpp/wiki/Tutorial

